title: @OspreyWTEN Heads to Fort Myers for Bedford Cup
text: 5' 10" Jr. FORT MYERS, Fla. â€“ The North Florida Women's Tennis team heads to Fort Myers for the annual Bedford Cup, taking place from Oct. 16-18 at the FGCU Tennis Complex. "We are excited for Bedford cup as it is a great opportunity to see some of the best college tennis players our state has to offer," says coach . "The girls have been working very hard and have shown resilience and determination in tough practice sessions for the last two weeks. Now is the time to believe in their work and enjoy the battle" The Ospreys will have all six players begin play at 8 a.m. on Friday in the singles round of 32.
